TERMINAL COMMANDS:
--------------------

List usb serial Devices: $ ls /dev/cu.usbserial*

List serial processes: $ lsof | grep usbserial

Kill process: $ kill [process id]

If that doesn't work:
Kill process: $ kill -9 [process id]

Run the main patch: $ python main_training_with_direct_loss.py --input-device 8 --port1 /dev/cu.usbserial-0001 --port2 /dev/cu.usbserial-2

Position the motors:
python position_motors.py --port1 /dev/cu.usbserial-0001 --port2 /dev/cu.usbserial-2

Run spectral loss:
python stft_audio.py --input-device 8 --channels 110

List audio devices:
python stft_audio.py --list 

Flags:

--skip-calibration Skip recalibration of motors initially and during reset


